content.rendered: Through the month of Ramadan, TTE team members got together for Iftar with blue-collar staff across the Emirates. Apart from breaking the fast by sharing the meal, the time spent together had a positive impact on everyone. Truly, the spirit of Ramadan lies in making a positive difference to everyone. The unsung heroes are the backbone of our operations, and their tireless dedication is the cornerstone of TTE’s success.
